title: Capital Returns!
subtitle: The capital strike has largely ended
view-if: capital_strike_seen and capital_strike_timer < 6 and not capital_flight and ((capital_strike_progress < (10-class_war)) or (not spd_in_government and capital_strike_progress < (15*bourgeois_power)))
new-page: true
tags: event
max-visits: 1
on-arrival: capital_strike_over = 1; capital_strike_progress *= 0.5; capital_strike_progress -= 5 if capital_strike_progress >= 10; economic_growth += 3*bourgeois_power; unemployed -= 3*bourgeois_power; workers_ddp += 2; workers_dvp += 2; new_middle_spd -= 3; old_middle_spd -= 3; rural_spd -= 3; {! 
if (Q.experimental_feature) {
    dendryUI.dendryEngine.state.visits.capital_strike = 0;
}
!}

The capital strike has come to an end, and Germany's economy begun to recover from the incident. [? if class_war : The revolutionary window of opportunity seems to have passed. ?]